Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.63,0:00:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大地上所有生命消失的审判之画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOST CANVAS 在天空展开的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哈迪斯城内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待着圣斗士天马的冥王的两位亲信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双子神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马 为了你能够将你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达给正在绘制这幅恐怖的画的亚伦哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也将和你一起战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.77,0:00:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的不安感究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着天马而去的这股邪恶而巨大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣战 现在正向新的局面发展
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(910,580}{\fad(500,0}第14话       死之森林
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那两个家伙跑得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么脚步都摇摇晃晃了？天马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了的话 我就为了你休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 累的人是你吧 耶人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少说梦话 我可没事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸上不是写着"让我休息一会"吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 居然敢骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 耶人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在打打闹闹了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要把你们两个都丢下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 让叶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打闹？谁会和这种家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 萨莎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就会潜入哈迪斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻底地结束这场圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉大人 哈迪斯大人到底在哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近完全看不到他的身影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪斯大人现在正在安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专心绘制LOST CANVAS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管太多了 切希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.22,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将哈迪斯大人软禁在画室里 是为了他好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让他尽快丢弃肮脏的人类之心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为完全的冥王觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈迪斯大人的那个微笑到底有什么含义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位大人正在那里等候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修普诺斯大人 达拿都斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召见我潘多拉 不知有何要事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该记得 我们说过 会亲手抹杀天马座这事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.15,0:05:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到冥界三巨头之一 拉达曼迪斯的小宇宙正在行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下达了什么命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有让拉达曼迪斯行动的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事我潘多拉并不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修普诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在意的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:06:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类是一种不值得倾注全部信赖的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们明明愚蠢 却有狡猾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对人类时 应当过份谨慎些才是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘多拉也是很清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些惹神明不悦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是没什么好处的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在天马座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到我部分力量的冥斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会热情地去迎接天马了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在200多年前的上一次圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜的圣斗士们在我们面前就像婴儿一样无力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次圣战一定要让我们尽兴才行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修普诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次像这样面会教皇是多少年前了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讽刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我见面之时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是将有灾难降于圣域之时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 本以为你坐上教皇之位后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就完全变迟钝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来拳法还没有衰退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那 不曾衰老的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再次觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的实力并不仅仅是白银圣斗士级别的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然老了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我的兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭坛星座白礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们兄弟并肩战斗的那场圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛就像昨天一般历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把黄金圣斗士的资格让给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为巨蟹座圣斗士和你一同突入冥王军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们失去了许多的同志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最终保护了这大地上的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但本该成为教皇的你却在两百多年间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在背后默默支持着圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不喜欢上台面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把一切都推给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对此深表歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本 祭坛座的使命便是辅助教皇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以每当圣域有不稳的征兆 你就会像这样来访
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通过人马座的希绪弗斯感受到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被某个巨大的小宇宙封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡神 修普诺斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 死神 达拿都斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为哈迪斯亲信的他们有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道冥王军发生了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他们是非常谨慎的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次圣战为了抓住他们的尾巴都费尽了力气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希绪弗斯为了调查他们跑遍了各地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕双子神是因此而记恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将被冥王所伤的希绪弗斯的灵魂封印到了某个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然双子神已经开始行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马他们就令人担心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次虽然被他们占了先机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次我们早有对策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不能预料到更先一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击败那双子神也就是天方夜谭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就祈祷他们武运长远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了胜利！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子 难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家小弟真会给人添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尼戈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道天马的行踪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下来正要被派去大老远的意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责看孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马他果然！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你小弟真让我觉得心烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管故乡被毁啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磨磨蹭蹭的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老头又会烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教皇知道这事了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马前往哈迪斯城的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管这些鸡零狗碎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那小弟是哈迪斯的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用价值很高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别冲动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为小弟着想的心情 我也不是不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是接近哈迪斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空就越是被LOST CANVAS所覆盖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惨不忍睹的景象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样和平的城镇被…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过这个镇子马上就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的故乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有这么片森林吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好阴森恐怖的森林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们必须前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气突破它！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成森林的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才起是不是就有股奇怪的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是什么腐烂的气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.18,0:13:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是骨头吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙搞什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 花环被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这臭鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴 别跑那么远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他们都消失了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连让叶都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你站住呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然耶人要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边跑一边留在树上的记号…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明记得这棵树上也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.32,0:14:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是天马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇突然起火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸也变得很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我来迟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为亚伦他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王军真的把大家都杀害了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 如果我们还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马的血 好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们的完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着呢 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马你还活着 我们很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们嫉妒啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然跑进那麻烦的森林里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸臭漫天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那森林可不是人类的产物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也许比较适合我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会说抓天马座 一会又说保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太会差遣人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞美诗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管风琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.74,0:16:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个白痴能在这种异常情况下若无其事地弹管风琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知您是否中意呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对您与挚爱亲友们的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管风琴可不能停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的好事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点解放他们啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是特地从冥界把他们带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得让他们好好派上用场才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就算解放他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也只会腐烂而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样岂不是更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要轰飞你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个傻孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将他的血肉全部吸干！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把那个管风琴想办法毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是冲着这管风琴来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁了这管风琴会有什么后果？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马流星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奉达拿都斯大人之命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护死亡森林的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.62,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳苏（NASU）是拜火教（祆教）的女恶魔，以苍蝇的形态出现。 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天究星的纳苏（NASU）维罗妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥斗士吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来告诉圣斗士先生您吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那种程度的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是管风琴还是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是不能伤到分毫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这管风琴被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些和你一起长大情同兄弟的孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变回普通的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也没关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们不是很痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是在哭吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙竟然为所欲为利用他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使他们被控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的灵魂并没有堕落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们再咬狠一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马彗星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的小宇宙是伤不到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没能保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能保护大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到天马说过的宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的成为圣斗士了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚伦他肯定也在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.81,0:22:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服都被血染脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有胆说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.45,0:22:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会放过的！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.05,0:24:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们闯入死之森林 迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飘散着各种死之符号的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能听见死者的声音 从某个地方传来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.25,0:24:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这个声音是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起令人怀念的我的故乡嘉米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢 The lost canvas  冥王神话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能回到那天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:15.17,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘自 赞美诗的第23首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:15.17,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶和华是我的牧者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:21.52,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必不至缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:32.26,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他使我躺卧在青草地上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:43.84,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领我在可安歇的水边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:54.46,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他使我的灵魂苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:17:10.18,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为自己的名引导我走义路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
